{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Follow</strong> and <strong>Wishlist</strong> our collection of weird fiction and cosmic horror stories:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/STEAM_231_87.png?t=1729167634\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/Nocturnes_231_87_01.png?t=1729167634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1729167634\" /><strong>!!!  All profits will be donated to help the victims of war in Ukraine  !!!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">^ click for more information</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/underline_02_620.png?t=1729167634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have you ever wondered what the master of weird fiction and cosmic horror might have <strong>dreamt about</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now you have the opportunity to immerse yourself in one of <strong>H. P. Lovecraft\u2019s nightmares</strong>, which he described in 1927 in a letter to Donald Wandrei - a co-founder of the famous Arkham House publishing house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So validate your ticket and find a comfortable seat - <strong>the motorman</strong> will be arriving shortly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/store_01.png?t=1729167634\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">get a glimpse into <strong>Lovecraft\u2019s dreams</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_para